  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK380">
<l>ūḻiṟ peruvali yāvuḷa maṟṟoṉṟu</l>
<l>cūḻiṉun tāṉmun tuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is stronger than fate ? If we think of an expedient (to avert it), it will itself be with us before (the thought).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
